    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227750/extras/0eb232b184c1444e2ae1bb64a434f97f.avif?t=1772378859\" width=625 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>Join Our Discord!</strong> 🏛️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step inside the arena and be part of something epic! By joining our Discord, you’ll get:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exclusive Alpha Tournaments</strong> : compete before anyone else!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Behind-the-Scenes Access</strong> :  follow our development journey up close.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Community-Only Contests</strong> : win prizes and special rewards just for being part of the community.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t just watch the action, <strong>be part of it</strong>. Join our Discord today and take your place in the arena! ⚔️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>SPARTACUS BLOOD ARENA - ALPHA</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Spartacus Blood Arena is an intense gladiator-themed combat game</strong>, developed by indie studio Survival Player in <strong>partnership with the archaeology departments and reenactors of Rome, Capua, and Pompeii.</strong> Step into the brutal world of ancient arenas where every fight is a battle for survival. Featuring historically inspired arenas and characters, this game brings to life <strong>the raw and unforgiving nature of gladiatorial combat</strong>. Customize your gladiator, master different fighting styles,(in development) and rise to glory in thrilling, visceral battles. Will you conquer the arena and earn your freedom, or fall to the sands of history? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227750/extras/22f58d958e8855a67e3ca8fe287da825.avif?t=1772378859\" width=800 height=558 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Authentic gladiator combat inspired by historical research.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Stunning arenas based on real locations in Rome, Capua, and Pompeii.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Deep customization options for your gladiator’s weapons and armor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Single-player campaign and multiplayer modes for epic battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Real-time combat system with brutal and dynamic fight mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227750/extras/d48863af5632884f7bb7330d93ec51b1.poster.avif?t=1772378859\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227750/extras/d48863af5632884f7bb7330d93ec51b1.webm?t=1772378859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227750/extras/d48863af5632884f7bb7330d93ec51b1.mp4?t=1772378859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong></strong><br><br><br><br><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pre-Alpha Stage – Spartacus: Blood Arena</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local and multiplayer modes are currently functional (story mode planned for the future). The game features 5 characters with partial customization options (still in development) and 6 environments.<br>Many aspects will be reworked in the next phase of the alpha, and we will release regular alpha update patches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227750/extras/c90eb5d20d5a4c6786ddeaccacadd173.poster.avif?t=1772378859\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227750/extras/c90eb5d20d5a4c6786ddeaccacadd173.webm?t=1772378859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227750/extras/c90eb5d20d5a4c6786ddeaccacadd173.mp4?t=1772378859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227750/extras/e37b81edcb851de0799481cdbf497e26.poster.avif?t=1772378859\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227750/extras/e37b81edcb851de0799481cdbf497e26.webm?t=1772378859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227750/extras/e37b81edcb851de0799481cdbf497e26.mp4?t=1772378859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
